item.title: CVE-2023-0061|2024-08-02T04:54:32.657Z -- unknown -- judge.me%20product%20reviews%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Judge.me Product Reviews for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 1.3.21 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
